---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Outreach - Project Prosthetic">
	<h1>Outreach & Support</h1>
	<p>Learn about organizations making a difference in prosthetic accessibility worldwide and discover how you can help support amputees in need.</p>
	
	<h2>Organizations Making a Difference</h2>
	<div class="organization-grid">
		<div class="organization-card international">
			<div class="card-header">
				<h3>ICRC in Afghanistan</h3>
				<span class="category">International Relief</span>
			</div>
			<p>ICRC provides prosthetic and orthotic services to thousands of Afghans, including those injured in conflict.</p>
			<a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/where-we-work/asia-pacific/afghanistan" target="_blank" class="learn-more">Learn More</a>
		</div>

		<div class="organization-card children">
			<div class="card-header">
				<h3>UNICEF in Gaza</h3>
				<span class="category">Children's Aid</span>
			</div>
			<p>UNICEF is launching a project to 3D print prosthetics for multiple injured children in the conflict.</p>
			<a href="https://www.unicef.org/emergencies/children-gaza-need-lifesaving-support" target="_blank" class="learn-more">Learn More</a>
		</div>

		<div class="organization-card veterans">
			<div class="card-header">
				<h3>Kind Deeds in the US</h3>
				<span class="category">Veterans Support</span>
			</div>
			<p>"Kind Deed In The US" offers Ukrainian war veterans prosthetic fittings and rehabilitation.</p>
			<a href="https://www.kinddeeds.org/" target="_blank" class="learn-more">Learn More</a>
		</div>

		<div class="organization-card equipment">
			<div class="card-header">
				<h3>Penta</h3>
				<span class="category">Equipment Access</span>
			</div>
			<p>Penta is a non-profit organization that repurposes second-hand and surplus medical equipment from the U.S. to bring high-quality, low-cost care to amputees.</p>
			<a href="https://pentaprosthetics.org/about-us/" target="_blank" class="learn-more">Learn More</a>
		</div>

		<div class="organization-card funding">
			<div class="card-header">
				<h3>Steps of Faith</h3>
				<span class="category">Funding Support</span>
			</div>
			<p>Steps of Faith helps amputees by raising funds and awareness to provide prosthetics for people who can't afford them, ensuring they get the mobility they need.</p>
			<a href="https://www.stepsoffaithfoundation.org/stories" target="_blank" class="learn-more">Learn More</a>
		</div>

		<div class="organization-card community">
			<div class="card-header">
				<h3>Amputee Coalition</h3>
				<span class="category">Community Support</span>
			</div>
			<p>The Amputee Coalition helps connect donors with people who need prosthetic limbs, creating a way for those with extra limbs to help others in need.</p>
			<a href="https://amputee-coalition.org/resources/prosthetic-limb-donations/" target="_blank" class="learn-more">Learn More</a>
		</div>

		<div class="organization-card children">
			<div class="card-header">
				<h3>Jordan Thomas Foundation</h3>
				<span class="category">Children's Aid</span>
			</div>
			<p>Provides prosthetics for kids in need, encouraging donations to help restore their independence and quality of life.</p>
			<a href="https://jtf.app.neoncrm.com/forms/give2025" target="_blank" class="learn-more">Learn More</a>
		</div>
	</div>

	<h2>Research & Educational Resources</h2>
	<div class="resources-section">
		<p style="color:black">To learn more about the issue, check these out!</p>
		<ul class="resource-list">
			<li>
				<strong>Prosthetic and Orthodontic International</strong>
				<p>Leading research and development in prosthetic technology worldwide</p>
        <p>
        </p>
        <a href="https://journals.lww.com/poijournal/fulltext/2022/02000/3d_printed_prostheses_in_developing_countries__a.5.aspx" target="_blank" class="learn-more">Learn More</a>
			</li>
			<li>
				<strong>South Dakota State University</strong>
				<p>Academic research on prosthetic accessibility and innovation</p>
        <p>
        </p>
        <a href="https://www.sdstate.edu/news/2024/05/engineering-students-design-affordable-prosthetics-help-amputees-war-torn-countries" target="_blank" class="learn-more">Learn More</a>
			</li>
			<li>  
				<strong>Access to prosthetic devices in developing countries: Pathways and challenges</strong>
				<p>Comprehensive study on global prosthetic accessibility barriers</p>
        <p>
        </p>
        <a href="https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/abstract/document/7343953?casa_token=aLEzY2BRAqkAAAAA:LnmzEBCvPxTHmibHRBKOPAkElSlNoOUIYAKJJFXVy5hLh2R9tl5ksx3hxgCds5GbMm3tZzY" target="_blank" class="learn-more">Learn More</a>
			</li>
		</ul>
	</div>

	<h2>How You Can Help</h2>
	<div class="action-section">
		<div class="action-card">
			<h3>ü§ù Volunteer</h3>
			<p>Many organizations need volunteers for fundraising, awareness campaigns, and direct support.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="action-card">
			<h3>üí∞ Donate</h3>
			<p>Financial contributions help provide prosthetics to those who cannot afford them.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="action-card">
			<h3>üì¢ Spread Awareness</h3>
			<p>Share information about these organizations and the challenges faced by amputees worldwide.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="action-card">
			<h3>üî¨ Support Research</h3>
			<p>Contribute to research initiatives that improve prosthetic technology and accessibility.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>

<style>
	h1, h2 {
		color: rgb(var(--accent));
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.organization-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
		gap: 1.5rem;
		margin: 2rem 0;
	}

	.organization-card {
		background: white;
		border-radius: 12px;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
		transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
		border-left: 4px solid;
	}

	.organization-card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-4px);
		box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
	}

	.organization-card.international {
		border-left-color: #e74c3c;
	}

	.organization-card.children {
		border-left-color: #f39c12;
	}

	.organization-card.veterans {
		border-left-color: #27ae60;
	}

	.organization-card.equipment {
		border-left-color: #3498db;
	}

	.organization-card.funding {
		border-left-color: #9b59b6;
	}

	.organization-card.community {
		border-left-color: #1abc9c;
	}

	.card-header {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: space-between;
		align-items: flex-start;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.card-header h3 {
		margin: 0;
		color: rgb(var(--accent-dark));
		font-size: 1.25rem;
	}

	.category {
		background: rgb(var(--accent-light));
		color: rgb(var(--accent-dark));
		padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
		border-radius: 20px;
		font-size: 0.8rem;
		font-weight: bold;
		white-space: nowrap;
	}

	.organization-card p {
		color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
		line-height: 1.6;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.learn-more {
		display: inline-block;
		background: rgb(var(--accent));
		color: white;
		padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
		text-decoration: none;
		border-radius: 6px;
		font-weight: bold;
		transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
	}

	.learn-more:hover {
		background: rgb(var(--accent-dark));
	}

	.resources-section {
		background: #f8f9fa;
		padding: 2rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
		margin: 2rem 0;
	}

	.resource-list {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
	}

	.resource-list li {
		background: white;
		padding: 1rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		border-radius: 8px;
		border-left: 4px solid rgb(var(--accent));
	}

	.resource-list strong {
		color: rgb(var(--accent-dark));
		display: block;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.resource-list p {
		margin: 0;
		color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
		font-size: 0.9rem;
	}

	.action-section {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
		gap: 1.5rem;
		margin: 2rem 0;
	}

	.action-card {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgb(var(--accent-light)), white);
		padding: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
		text-align: center;
		border: 1px solid rgba(var(--accent), 0.2);
	}

	.action-card h3 {
		color: rgb(var(--accent-dark));
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
	}

	.action-card p {
		color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
		margin: 0;
		line-height: 1.5;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.organization-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.card-header {
			flex-direction: column;
			align-items: flex-start;
		}

		.category {
			margin-top: 0.5rem;
		}

		.action-section {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}
</style>